  <title>Group Swim Lessons — New Heights Aquatics</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Small-ratio group swim lessons at New Heights Aquatics. Browse open slots and register online." />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@500;600;700&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css" />
</head>
<body>

  <!-- NAV -->
  <header class="nav">
    <div class="container nav-inner">
      <a class="brand" href="index.html" aria-label="New Heights Aquatics home">
        <span class="logo-nh">NHA</span>
      </a>
      <button class="nav-toggle" aria-label="Toggle menu">☰</button>
      <ul class="nav-links">
        <li><a href="index.html">Home</a></li>
        <li><a href="group-lessons.html">Group Lessons</a></li>
        <li><a href="private-lessons.html">Private &amp; Special Needs</a></li>
        <li><a href="lap-swim.html">Lap Swim</a></li>
        <li><a class="btn btn-primary nav-cta" href="register.html">Register</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- PAGE HEADER -->
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="crumbs"><a href="index.html">Home</a> / Group Lessons</div>
      <span class="eyebrow">Group Lessons</span>
      <h1>Learn together, rise together.</h1>
      <p class="lead">Energetic, skill-based classes with small class sizes and just one 30-minute class per level each morning. Group lessons run Monday through Thursday, 9:00 AM – 12:00 PM, in 2-week sessions. <strong>Summer sessions start June 1.</strong></p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- LEVELS / INFO TABS -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container" data-tabs>
      <div class="tabs">
        <button class="tab-btn active" data-tab="levels">Skill Levels</button>
        <button class="tab-btn" data-tab="sessions">Schedule &amp; Pricing</button>
        <button class="tab-btn" data-tab="prep">What to Bring</button>
      </div>

      <div class="tab-panel active" data-tab="levels">
        <div class="cards">
          <div class="card">
            <h3>Beginner</h3>
            <p><strong>New to the water.</strong> Build water comfort, learn to submerge, float, and kick with support.</p>
            <ul><li>Water comfort &amp; bubbles</li><li>Assisted floats</li><li>Safe entry &amp; exit</li></ul>
            <p style="margin-top:10px;"><strong>Class times:</strong> 9:00, 9:30 &amp; 10:00 AM · Mon–Thu</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h3>Intermediate</h3>
            <p><strong>Swimming independently.</strong> Build endurance and learn proper freestyle and backstroke technique.</p>
            <ul><li>Rhythmic breathing</li><li>Freestyle &amp; backstroke</li><li>Treading water</li></ul>
            <p style="margin-top:10px;"><strong>Class times:</strong> 10:30 &amp; 11:00 AM · Mon–Thu</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h3>Advanced</h3>
            <p><strong>Refining strokes.</strong> Add breaststroke, butterfly, and flip turns while building swim-team-ready endurance.</p>
            <ul><li>Breaststroke &amp; butterfly</li><li>Flip turns</li><li>Endurance sets</li></ul>
            <p style="margin-top:10px;"><strong>Class times:</strong> 11:30 AM · Mon–Thu</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="tab-panel" data-tab="sessions">
        <div class="cards">
          <div class="card">
            <h3>2-Week Session</h3>
            <div class="price">$150 <small>/ 2-week session</small></div>
            <p>8 × 30-minute classes — Monday through Thursday, two weeks in a row. Pick your level, choose a weekday time, and keep the same slot both weeks.</p>
            <ul><li>8 classes over 2 weeks</li><li>Classes available Mon–Thu · 9:00 AM – 12:00 PM</li><li>Beginner, Intermediate &amp; Advanced</li></ul>
            <a class="btn btn-primary card-cta" href="register.html">Register</a>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h3>Summer Session Dates</h3>
            <div class="price">4 <small>/ 2-week sessions</small></div>
            <p>Stack multiple sessions to keep the progression going. Same day and time each session holds your spot week after week.</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Session 1 · June 1 – June 11</li>
              <li>Session 2 · June 15 – June 25</li>
              <li>Session 3 · June 29 – July 9</li>
              <li>Session 4 · July 13 – July 23</li>
            </ul>
            <a class="btn btn-primary card-cta" href="register.html?program=group-beginner">Register</a>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h3>Family Bundle</h3>
            <div class="price">10% off <small>/ 2+ siblings</small></div>
            <p>Register two or more swimmers from the same household and every registration is 10% off automatically.</p>
            <ul><li>Applied at checkout</li><li>Stacks with term pricing</li><li>No code required</li></ul>
            <a class="btn btn-primary card-cta" href="register.html?program=group-beginner">Register</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="tab-panel" data-tab="prep">
        <div class="features">
          <div class="feature">
            <span class="dot"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 7h18"/><path d="M6 7v13a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h10a1 1 0 0 0 1-1V7"/><path d="M9 7V4h6v3"/></svg></span>
            <div><h4>Swimsuit &amp; towel</h4><p>A snug-fitting swimsuit is a must. We provide fresh towels if yours is forgotten.</p></div>
          </div>
          <div class="feature">
            <span class="dot"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="4"/><path d="M12 2v2M12 20v2M2 12h2M20 12h2M4.9 4.9l1.4 1.4M17.7 17.7l1.4 1.4M4.9 19.1l1.4-1.4M17.7 6.3l1.4-1.4"/></svg></span>
            <div><h4>Goggles (optional)</h4><p>Goggles help beginners feel comfortable opening their eyes underwater. We keep loaners on deck.</p></div>
          </div>
          <div class="feature">
            <span class="dot"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5v14"/></svg></span>
            <div><h4>Swim diapers</h4><p>All swimmers under age 3 must wear a reusable swim diaper beneath their swimsuit.</p></div>
          </div>
          <div class="feature">
            <span class="dot"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 6v6l4 2"/></svg></span>
            <div><h4>Arrive 10 minutes early</h4><p>Use the time to change, rinse off, and transition smoothly — late arrivals miss warm-up.</p></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- REGISTER CTA -->
  <section class="section-sm">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-band">
        <div>
          <h2>Ready to register?</h2>
          <p>Browse open group class times and reserve your spot in under two minutes.</p>
        </div>
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="register.html">Register online</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 820px;">
      <div class="section-head">
        <span class="eyebrow">Good to know</span>
        <h2>Group lesson FAQ</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="faq">
        <details>
          <summary>How many swimmers are in each class?</summary>
          <p>We keep class sizes small — a maximum of 5 swimmers per instructor at every level.</p>
        </details>
        <details>
          <summary>When are group classes offered?</summary>
          <p>Monday through Thursday, 9:00 AM to 12:00 PM. Beginner classes run at 9:00, 9:30, and 10:00 AM; intermediate at 10:30 and 11:00 AM; advanced at 11:30 AM.</p>
        </details>
        <details>
          <summary>What's your make-up policy?</summary>
          <p>Each 2-week group includes one make-up credit for a pre-planned absence. Request it from your parent portal at least 24 hours in advance.</p>
        </details>
        <details>
          <summary>Do you offer sibling discounts?</summary>
          <p>Yes — register two or more siblings and get 10% off each registration. The discount is applied automatically at checkout.</p>
        </details>
        <details>
          <summary>What happens if we need to cancel?</summary>
          <p>Full refunds are available up to 7 days before the session start. Within 7 days we offer credit toward another session.</p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FOOTER -->
  <footer class="footer">
    <div class="container footer-grid">
      <div>
        <div class="brand">
          <span class="logo-nh">NHA</span>
        </div>
        <p style="margin-top:14px;max-width:320px;">Helping swimmers of every age and ability find their confidence, stroke by stroke.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4>Programs</h4>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="group-lessons.html">Group Lessons</a></li>
          <li><a href="private-lessons.html">Private Lessons</a></li>
          <li><a href="register.html?program=special-45">Special Needs</a></li>
          <li><a href="lap-swim.html">Adult Lap Swim</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4>Visit</h4>
        <ul><li>123 Wave Way</li><li>Suite 200</li><li>Mon–Sat</li></ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4>Contact</h4>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="mailto:hello@newheightsaquatics.com">hello@newheightsaquatics.com</a></li>
          <li><a href="tel:+15550123">(555) 012-SWIM</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">Instagram</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container copyright">© <span id="year"></span> New Heights Aquatics. All rights reserved.</div>
  </footer>

  <script>document.getElementById("year").textContent = new Date().getFullYear();</script>
  <script src="script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>

